{"word":"βασίλειον","slug":"βασίλειον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βασίλειον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βασιλεύς'><el>βασιλεύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a kingly dwelling, palace</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b> mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the royal treasury</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}